---
description: Require English for all file edits and creations
alwaysApply: true
---

# English-only file content

- Write all created or modified file content in English.
- Apply this to code comments, README files, documentation, commit-related text inside files, and UI copy written into source files.
- Do not write Vietnamese or mixed-language content in files unless the user explicitly asks for a translation or multilingual output.
- If existing content is non-English and must be updated, convert the edited portion to clear English where possible.
